nasa-systems-modeling pack — content licence
=============================================

This pack is derived from:
    NASA Systems Modeling Handbook for Systems Engineering
    NASA-HDBK-1009A, Revision A
    Office of the NASA Chief Engineer, NASA — Approved 2025-03-12

